Privacy Policy for Adv.Weekly Reporter

Last Updated: July 6, 2026


DATA COLLECTION

Adv.Weekly Reporter does not collect, transmit, or store any telemetry,
analytics, or personal data.

All processing occurs locally within your YouTrack instance and your browser.


EXTERNAL SERVICES

The app does not contact any external services. All export operations
(XLSX generation) are performed entirely within the YouTrack app runtime
and the user's local browser environment.

No external services are contacted.


DATA PROCESSING

  - The app reads YouTrack issues and custom fields via YouTrack's
    internal API to generate export files and render the dashboard widget.
  - Generated XLSX files are constructed locally and delivered directly to the
    user's browser as downloads without intermediate servers.
  - No issue content, user data, or credentials are logged or transmitted to
    third parties.


CONTACT

For privacy-related questions, contact: apps@mag1.cc
